REDIRECTION 
-----------
#uptime >/dev/ops/temp     >>>>>>content of uptime is copy to file
#uptime>>/dev/ops/temp     >>>>>>overwrite

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PIPE
----
ls | wc -l        >>>>>> output of list is fed to count 
ls | grep akhil   >>>>>> out of list fed to grep to search word akhil
tail -20 /var/log/messages | grep -i akhil   >>>>>> search akhil in last 20 lines of that file



